quran[7{c,v,t}:
7,131,"magar unn ka haal yeh tha ke jab acha zamana aata to kehte ke hum isi ke mustahiq hain, aur jab bura zamana aata to moose aur is ke sathiyon ko apne liye faal -e-badtehratay, halaank Dur haqeeqat un ki faal bad to Allah ke paas thi, magar un mein se aksar be ilm thay"
7,132,"unhon ne moose se kaha ke"" to hamein mashooor karne ke liye khuwa koi nishani le aeye, hum to teri baat maan-ne walay nahi hain """
7,133,"aakhir-kaar hum ne un par tufaan bheja, tiddi dil chhorey,sursuryan philayin, maindak nikalay, aur khoo noon barsaya yeh sab nishanain allag allag kar ke deikhein, magar woh sir kashi kiye chalay gay aur woh barray hi mujrim log thay"
7,134,"jab kabhi unn par bulaa nazil ho jati to kehte"" ae moose, tujhe apne rab ki taraf se jo mansab haasil hai is ki bana par hamaray haq mein dua kar, agar ab ke to hum par se yeh bulaa Talwa day to hum teri baat maan len ge aur bani Israel ko tairay sath bhaij den ge """
7,135,"magar jab hum un par se apna azaab aik waqt muqarrar taq ke liye, jis ko woh behar haal pounchanay walay thay, hata letay to woh yklkht apne ehad se phir jatay"
7,136,tab hum ne unn se intiqam liya aur inhen samandar mein ghark kar diya kyunkay unhon ne hamari nshanyon ko jhtlaya tha aur unn se be parwa ho gay thay
7,137,"aur unn ki jagah hum ne unn logon ko jo kamzor bana kar rakhay gay thay, uss sarzamen ke mashriq o maghrib ka waris bana diya jisay hum ne barkatoon se malaa maal kya tha is terhan bani Israel ke haq mein tairay rab ka wada kher poora howa kyunkay onhon ne sabr se kaam liya tha aur firaon aur is ki qoum ka woh sab kuch barbaad kar diya gaya jo woh banatay aur charhatay thay"
